Detailed Description

Polynomial represents a finite order polynomial with positive powers and constant real coefficients.

The polynomial coefficients are ordered such that c[0] is the constant term and c[n] is the coefficient of z^n, that is y = c[0]*x^0+c[1]*x^1+c[2]*x^2+...
